<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mock Payment Success</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; background-color: #f0f8f0; }
        .container { text-align: center; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .badge { background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: inline-block; }
        h1 { color: #28a745; }
        p { color: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">MOCK PAYMENT</div>
        <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        <p>Your payment for order <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> was successful.</p>
        <p>Amount: {{amount}} RUB via {{provider}}</p>
        <p>You can now close this window.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
